      "content": "i get what you're saying about patterns but it felt way more intentional than that. like the person wasn't even reacting to the environment, just kind of... repeating a sequence. i've been reading about simulation theory and some of these 'glitches' people talk about sound exactly like what i just saw. do u think it's actually possible we're living in some kind of processed environment that's starting to hit some kind of resource limit or something?",
